Sentencas: In this work, low polarization resistance heterostructure cathode is constructed through (Ni,Fe) exsolution from Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-delta and following in-situ re-oxidation and precipitation as (Ni,Fe)O nano particles.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The heterostructure effectively promotes oxygen reduction reaction, and decreases polarization resistance by similar to 50% with smallest R-p of 0.084 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C, which is among the better Cobalt & Lanthanide-free cathodes.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Moreover, the cathode performance is prominently optimized under low temperatures and low oxygen partial pressures, yielding smaller activation energy and lower oxygen partial pressure dependence (R-p, (650 degrees c)proportional to(p(O2))(0.28)).
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Further, the heterostructure cathode is successfully fabricated in Ni-Fe supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell, using whole-cell-reduction and cathode re-oxidation strategies.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The cell exhibits maximum electrical power density of 740 mW/cm(2) at 750 degrees C, with Ni-YSZ anode and YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Electrical efficiencies over similar to 90% at operation potential above 0.75 V are obtained, showing highly efficient operation in wide range of temperatures.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: This is a successfully trial by coupling low-cost and high-performance cathode with metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell.
Titulo: Coupling decreased polarization resistance Sr0.95Ti0.3Fe0.6Ni0.1O3-δ cathode with efficient metal supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
